<li><a href="Wikipedia_BRD_misuse" title="Wikipedia:BRD misuse">Wikipedia:BRD misuse</a> for a contrary position</li>
<li><a href="Wikipedia_Revert_only_when_necessary" title="Wikipedia:Revert only when necessary">Wikipedia:Revert only when necessary</a></li>
<li><a href="Wikipedia_Don't_revert_due_to_%22no_consensus%22" title="Wikipedia:Don't revert due to &quot;no consensus&quot;" class="mw-redirect">Wikipedia:Don't revert due to "no consensus"</a></li>
<li><a href="Wikipedia_Method_for_consensus_building" title="Wikipedia:Method for consensus building">Wikipedia:Method for consensus building</a></li>
