<li><a href="Minority_influence" title="Minority influence">Minority influence</a></li>
<li><a href="Twelve_Angry_Men_(Westinghouse_Studio_One)" title="Twelve Angry Men (Westinghouse Studio One)">Twelve Angry Men (Westinghouse Studio One)</a> or <a href="12_Angry_Men_(1997_film)" title="12 Angry Men (1997 film)">12 Angry Men (1997 film)</a>: A movie in which one of the characters (the architect) applies a variant on BRD in a "real life" jury. The architect finds the position of each of the other jury members in turn, enters discussion with that jury member, and thus over time manages to convince the jury to acquit the accused.</li>
</ul>


